{"tid":2156423,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"姊弟戀性虐案押後裁決 控方指事主是「愛的俘虜」飽受虐待及暴力對待","createTime":"2020-08-14T12:10:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T13:17:33.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0aed502b323b1710be49cfe40eba08f1ce2c428d","tid":2156423,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T12:10:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200814/XIMKHESFW5GONCC742YI6G7X7E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200814%2FXIMKHESFW5GONCC742YI6G7X7E%2F&d=NZlAC2w8bMplDXSravNUcTKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=ed78d90d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200814%2FXIMKHESFW5GONCC742YI6G7X7E%2F&h=e1ba63ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200814/XIMKHESFW5GONCC742YI6G7X7E/</a><br />\n<br />\n32歲初戀處男疑遭姊弟戀女友性虐案今審結。控辯雙方結案陳詞時披露，案件開審前曾替男事主索取精神科報告，以證明事主沒有精神問題。控方指男事主對女友付出無條件的愛，卻承受對方的虐待、壓迫及暴力對待，形容在整段「有毒關係」之中，男事主成了「愛的俘虜」；辯方則指，專家報告認為事主傷勢似自殘造成，控方未能證明傷勢一定由女被告造成。案件押後至9月25日裁決。"},{"pid":"e467c80825abf7604f2d8e23b61b3e18b6fb2360","tid":2156423,"uid":91017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T12:19:47.000Z","msg":"姐姐的專用牛奶肉棒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ff433982867225f46159602488aac3aaab52fb1","tid":2156423,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T13:17:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/警亂作供統計-至少-21-案罪成不成立-因警作供不獲接納-官屢批不可信-狡辯-不誠實/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E8%AD%A6%E4%BA%82%E4%BD%9C%E4%BE%9B%E7%B5%B1%E8%A8%88-%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%91-21-%E6%A1%88%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%E4%B8%8D%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B-%E5%9B%A0%E8%AD%A6%E4%BD%9C%E4%BE%9B%E4%B8%8D%E7%8D%B2%E6%8E%A5%E7%B4%8D-%E5%AE%98%E5%B1%A2%E6%89%B9%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E4%BF%A1-%E7%8B%A1%E8%BE%AF-%E4%B8%8D%E8%AA%A0%E5%AF%A6%2F&d=NZlAC2w8bMplDX